會有拒絕人嘅勇氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T19:16:29.000Z","msg":"但拒絕完成日都會好大內疚感 又會驚呢樣驚嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:50:38.000Z","msg":"但係其實本來件事就唔係你嘅責任 <br />\n所以其實唔需要太內疚<br />\n當然呢種諗法要時間改變<br />\n我都努力中<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af29f04fd5e452634d5756c9267c851bf612cdf8","tid":2450873,"uid":392873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7d695810506289c56f75d080f217a5d9ffe8903","tid":2450873,"uid":5301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee5dd37928a112bab1908782fd243dcd374ec614","tid":2450873,"uid":392873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd8452a4a67ae7b18fecf12f964ae57cb3f8399","tid":2450873,"uid":5301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T19:19:26.000Z","msg":"都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實諗諗下都唔太明點解自己要咁執著令所有人都鐘意自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T19:36:24.000Z","msg":"咁樣好辛苦 我都改變緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T19:44:04.000Z","msg":"咁嘅性格的確有令多咗人鐘意自己 多咗朋友 有啲好嘅朋友會識欣賞返你嘅好 但總有啲衰人成日得寸進尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最近開始愈嚟愈頂唔順 好撚想改 做個自私嘅人好似仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"明明人生係自己既 做咩要委屈自己呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}